4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become an AI Machine Learning Engineer". This course aims to help students start a career as a data scientist and build their first machine learning models. The course lasts for 16 weeks and includes 3 classes weekly. The class size is limited to 12 people. No previous experience is required to enroll in the course. The instructors for this course include Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena - all of whom have extensive experience in the field of AI and machine learning. Students will learn Python, SQL, and various libraries such as Pandas and Numpy to create predictive models. Additionally, students will practice solving real-life cases and develop their own AI projects. The course is available in English or Spanish. Upon completion, students will receive a certificate recognized by multiple organizations. For more information, visit the 4Geeks Academy website at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop